        "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe `custom-tags` test in [packages/twoslash/test/rich.test.ts](cci:7://file:///Users/rajattiwari/shiki/packages/twoslash/test/rich.test.ts:0:0-0:0) was failing because the code sample contained imports (`shiki/core`, `shiki/engine/javascript`) that could not be resolved in the test environment. \r\n\r\nThis PR fixes the failure by adding `// @noErrors` to the code sample, which suppresses the module resolution errors while keeping the test logic intact.\r\n\r\n### Linked Issues\r\n\r\nFixes #1167\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\ncc @antfu ",
